<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Integrate - Solicitud correcta</title>
    <link href='https://unpkg.com/boxicons@2.1.4/css/boxicons.min.css' rel='stylesheet'>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="<%= getFile('global/css/styles.css') %>">
    <style>
        .error-page {
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 2rem;
            text-align: center;
            background-color: var(--light-gray);
        }

        .error-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            padding: 3rem;
            background-color: var(--white);
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 5rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: var(--text-color);
        }

        .error-message {
            color: var(--text-light);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .return-btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: var(--border-radius-md);
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all var(--transition-normal);
        }

        .return-btn:hover {
            background-color: var(--primary-dark);
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        @media (max-width: 576px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 2rem;
            }

            .error-icon {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .error-message {
                font-size: 1rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('header') %>

    <main class="error-page">
        <div class="error-container">
            <i class='bx bx-check-circle error-icon'></i>
            <h1 class="error-title">Â¡PERFECTO!</h1>
            <p class="error-message">Tu solicitud de ha enviado correctamente. Nos estaremos comunicando a la brevedad, para finalizar el proceso de registro.</p>
            <a href="/" class="return-btn">VOLVER AL INICIO</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('footer') %>
</body>
</html>